{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"C-lite 执行时序\n      \nScheduler\n  → wake Loop Agent\nLoop Agent\n  → Kernel: assemble stable context\n  → RecruitingWorldStateProvider: query DB snapshot\n  → MemoryIndexProvider: list relevant memory indices\n  → LLM: decide next actions\n  → if need detail:\n       MemoryDetailReader: read selected detail\n       LLM: refine action\n  → RecruitingActionAdapter / WorkerRuntime\n       - enqueue run / call skill / write business data\n  → EventBus / Approval / SleepPolicy\n  → return next wake condition\n\n        特点：世界状态直接来自招聘 DB；memory 是两阶段；Loop tick 是独立的，不依赖长消息历史。","choice":"c-lite-seq","id":null,"timestamp":1776407713589}
