{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"通用 Agent OS 执行时序\n      \nScheduler（调度器）\n  → wake Loop Agent（唤醒 Loop Agent）\nLoop Agent（顶层 Agent）\n  → Universal Kernel: fetch generic world state（取通用世界状态）\n  → WorldState Normalizer: map recruiting data into universal entities（把招聘数据标准化成通用实体）\n  → Generic Memory Store: retrieve context（从通用记忆层取上下文）\n  → LLM: decide next actions（决定下一步动作）\n  → Generic Action Bus（通用动作总线）\n       → Recruiting plugin rehydrates business meaning（招聘插件还原业务语义）\n       → enqueue run / call skill / write data（入队执行 / 调 skill / 改数据）\n  → Universal Event / Approval / Sleep（通用事件 / 审批 / 休眠）\n  → return next wake condition（返回下次唤醒条件）\n\n        特点：先抽象成通用状态，再还原回招聘语义；理论更统一，但中间多了一层翻译层。","choice":"generic-seq","id":null,"timestamp":1776407942321}
